{"tid":1792924,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"越嚟越難叫雞係因為狼來了","createTime":"2019-12-22T04:20:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-22T05:12:56.000Z","uid":3522,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d9613e8cbcdf9be0294ce70faae37e05fd1bf7ff","tid":1792924,"uid":3522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T04:20:37.000Z","msg":"相信近排吹極雞都好小人嘅其中一個原因係狼來了<br />\n前排有班撚樣瘋狂推黎明行動 就算有好多人反對都繼續推<br />\n會推黎明po嘅相信有三種人<br />\n<br />\n1.會實行黎明行動嘅人<br />\n2.冷氣軍師<br />\n3.想被罷工但係又唔出嘅仆街冚家鏟<br />\n<br />\n問題就出喺後面兩種人到<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反對嘅當然唔會推po同出<br />\n而呢兩種人不斷推po令人以為黎明行動會有好多人參與<br />\n但點知個個得把口唔會出 令到大家對啲吹雞失去信心<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我諗到嘅解決方法就係自己真係會出先推po<br />\n然後再跟據留言數同正皮數決定個行動搞唔搞<br />\n相信咁樣run一排之後大家會對吹雞有返啲信心 響應人數都會多返<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55f0cedad9074445c6caa09dfa2362e38df87787","tid":1792924,"uid":49018,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T04:21:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5zjT1qE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5zjT1qE.jpg&h=f1f65c75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今日三點半，麻煩大家準時！<br />\n現場唔好有連豬，連狗<br />\n尊重返人哋啲宗教<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TAHBZcu.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTAHBZcu.gif&h=f5f36c0c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zpRGqSx.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzpRGqSx.gif&h=bc12f105&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n另外，&Ouml;zil畀人屌到屎眼爛都冇跪<br />\n我哋聽日都要支持佢<br />\n<br />\nStand with Uyghur(We ga）, Stand with &Ouml;zil（奧燒）"},{"pid":"ee4d4222b614843f85cc0715f732dd8c1f7d8787","tid":1792924,"uid":170014,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T04:23:50.000Z","msg":"我覺得係因為支線太多 活動太散 文宣不足 籌備唔夠"},{"pid":"403aede30ab7e45aad42fcc6648da708fa6e0f1b","tid":1792924,"uid":37733,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T04:31:00.000Z","msg":"叫咩野雞"},{"pid":"1ea833cecf2eb2a7c6ac973b8b3ca94119e1995b","tid":1792924,"uid":223399,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T04:34:59.000Z","msg":"咁樣諗太理想<br />\n嗰兩班撚樣永遠當無成本咁叫人出嚟<br />\n但其實黎明行動嘅風險係好高<br />\n同有時一早落到去啲手足先得小貓三四隻"},{"pid":"dc78af67698813d265aa1068672c50fa4ecf9b3e","tid":1792924,"uid":3522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"403aede30ab7e45aad42fcc6648da708fa6e0f1b","tid":1792924,"uid":37733,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T04:31:00.000Z","msg":"叫咩野雞"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T04:37:30.000Z","msg":"打錯 吹雞先啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"648c67c3f93f58cd061a98c588012a8dcba4808e","tid":1792924,"uid":3522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee4d4222b614843f85cc0715f732dd8c1f7d8787","tid":1792924,"uid":170014,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T04:23:50.000Z","msg":"我覺得係因為支線太多 活動太散 文宣不足 籌備唔夠"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T04:40:11.000Z","msg":"呢個都係其中一個原因"},{"pid":"a45a4cdc5f624964939f2d1b2f43d316f6ed7e1c","tid":1792924,"uid":3522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1ea833cecf2eb2a7c6ac973b8b3ca94119e1995b","tid":1792924,"uid":223399,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T04:34:59.000Z","msg":"咁樣諗太理想<br />\n嗰兩班撚樣永遠當無成本咁叫人出嚟<br />\n但其實黎明行動嘅風險係好高<br />\n同有時一早落到去啲手足先得小貓三四隻"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T04:44:07.000Z","msg":"我呢個方法只可靠大家自律<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e28c49685ad618156d63822658c9534669ee3c2","tid":1792924,"uid":66719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T04:44:59.000Z","msg":"你算漏左有一大班五毛係到推波助瀾"},{"pid":"d8b